{"title":"借助 Safari 调试苹果手机上的 webView","date":"2018-07-25T07:21:07.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 25, 2018","L":"07/25/2018","MM-DD":"07-25"},"link":"2018/debug-webview-with-safari","comments":true,"tags":["webView"],"categories":["iOS"],"updated":"2022-09-02T06:38:13.687Z","content":"<h2 id=\"iphone-真机/模拟器设置\">iPhone 真机/模拟器设置<a title=\"#iphone-真机/模拟器设置\" href=\"#iphone-真机/模拟器设置\"></a></h2>\n<p>需要如下图所示，点击“设置” → 点击 “Safari 浏览器” → 点击“高级” → 打开“Web 检查器”。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p><img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/open-the-web-inspector.jpg\" alt=\"打开 Web 检查器\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>若模拟器中无“Web 检查器”选项，无需设置。</p>\n<h2 id=\"safari-设置\">Safari 设置<a title=\"#safari-设置\" href=\"#safari-设置\"></a></h2>\n<p>打开 Mac 电脑中的 Safari 浏览器，打开偏好设置，点击菜单中的“高级”选项卡，勾选“在菜单栏中显示“开发”菜单”</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/safari-perferences-advanced.jpg\" alt=\"Safari-偏好设置-高级\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"进入检查器\">进入检查器<a title=\"#进入检查器\" href=\"#进入检查器\"></a></h2>\n<p>在手机/模拟器中打开浏览器/App 中的某个网页，在 Mac 中打开 Safari，在“开发”中找到目标设备。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/select-target-device.jpg\" alt=\"选择目标设备\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>如果你选择的是模拟器，但是开发列表中未出现，重启 Safari 即可。因为必须确保先打开模拟器，再打开 Safari。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>点击目标设备中需要查看的网址，便会弹出这个页面对应的检查器。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/web-inspector.jpg\" alt=\"网页检查器\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"在 Mac 上为 Git 和终端设置代理","link":"2018/set-up-sock5-or-http-proxy-for-git-on-mac"},"next":{"title":"App Store 审核经验","link":"2018/review-experience"},"plink":"https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/","toc":[{"id":"iphone-真机/模拟器设置","title":"iPhone 真机&#x2F;模拟器设置","index":"1"},{"id":"safari-设置","title":"Safari 设置","index":"2"},{"id":"进入检查器","title":"进入检查器","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"FiTeen","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/\" title=\"借助 Safari 调试苹果手机上的 webView\">https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}